reviewText:
Pom Pom Girls is fifty minutes and was released in 1995. I have no idea as to why it was called Pom Pom Girls as there are no pom pom girls in the video. I found the video disappointing. Throughout the video the girls are mainly fondling their breasts, flirting, and teasing in front of the camera. Only about ten minutes of Pom Pom Girls do we see in the nude. Five of the ten minutes is between a female student and her male teacher has a nude sex scene making out. There are a bunch of topless scenes, but found them boring. Only two of the girls introduced showed any nudity at all. Pom Pom Girls gets a D+.
